        "2 & 3 & 1 \\\\\n",
        "1 & 4 & 0 \\\\\n",
        "3 & 2 & 0 \\\\\n",
        "\\end{bmatrix}$$\n",
        "\n",
        "We will expand the matrix over the third column:\n",
        "\n",
        "$$\\det B = +1\\cdot \\det \\begin{bmatrix} 1 & 4 \\\\ 3 & 2\\end{bmatrix} = 2 - 12 = -10$$\n",
        "\n"
